headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Welltower (WELL) After Its Strong Multi‑Year Rally?
summary: If you are wondering whether Welltower is still good value after its strong run, or if the price already reflects the story, this article walks through what the current share price might be implying. With the stock at US$185.65, Welltower has been flat over the last 7 days, down 7.6% over the last month, and roughly in line year to date.
